<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉nạ qlby ysjd lyk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr
 - ạ̉nạ qlby ysjd lyk wlsạny yrnm byk

[V2]
 ḥbk kẖly̱ ḥyạty tbqy̱ lyk trnymẗ sẖkr

[V3]
 1- tsbyḥ mn ạlṭywr byʿlạlk wạlkwn ysẖhd lʿẓmtk wjlạlk

[V4]
 lạzm tsbyḥnạ yʿly̱ ʿnhm wybqy̱ ạḥly̱ ạ̹nt msẖ bs kẖạlqtnạ ạnt fạdynạ

[V5]
 2- wfy kl mrẗ bḥkylk brtạḥ bfrḥ lmạ mʿạk bftḥ qlby

[V6]
 lkn frḥy bykbr lmạ brnm wbsẖkr ʿsẖạn ạ̹nt bqyt ạ̉gẖly̱ mn ḥyạty

[V7]
 3- fwq tsbyḥ ạlṭywr ạ̉ʿly̱ mn ạ̉y swr ạ̹ṭlq tsbyḥy lyk fy ḥyạty

[V8]
 mhmạ kạnt ẓrwfy zạdt ạ̉sbạb lkẖwfy ạ̉nạ frḥy fyk tẖạbt ṭwl ạyạmy</lyrics>
<author>mynạ jmyl, mynạ jmyl</author>
<hymn_number>5918</hymn_number>
</song>